prodNameC: 免疫特 游離前列腺特異性抗原試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Free PSA Test Units (LPF1):
Each barcode-labeled unit contains one bead coated with monoclonal murine anti-PSA antibody specific for free (uncomplexed) PSA. 
Free PSA Reagent Wedges (LPFA, LPFB):
LPFA: 6.5 mL of a protein buffer matrix, with preservative.
LPFB: 6.5 mL alkaline phosphatase (bovine calf intestine) conjugated to polyclonal goat anti-PSA antibody specific for PSA in a buffer containing human serum
Free PSA Adjustors (LPFL, LPFH):
Two vials (Low and High) of lyophilized free PSA in a buffer solution.
applicantAddr: 台北市南港區園區街３號８樓
efficacy: 定量檢測血清中游離的、未結合的前列腺特異性抗原(PSA)。
